title: Lila Mae Swanson -- Rochester
maintext:
Lila Mae (Hennum) Swanson, 86, of Rochester, passed away on Wednesday, April 17, 2019, at Samaritan Bethany on 8th.
Lila was born on May 24, 1932, in Wanamingo, to Arthur and Ragna Hennum. She had two sisters, Ruby and Sylvia. On May 17, 1952, she married Paul Swenson. He died on June 17, 1993. Lila was a department manager at IBM and an active member of Bethel Lutheran Church.
She is survived by nieces and nephews in Florida, Illinois, and Indiana; and many friends.
There will be a private graveside service held in Pine Island.
